Otten JDM(1), Fracheboud J(2), den Heeten GJ(3), Otto SJ(2), Holland R(3), de 
Koning HJ(2), Broeders MJM(4), Verbeek ALM(5).

Author information:
(1)Department for Health Evidence, Radboud University Medical Centre, Nijmegen. 
Electronic address: j.otten@ebh.umcn.nl.
(2)Department of Public Health, Erasmus Medical Center, University Medical 
Center Rotterdam, Rotterdam.
(3)National Expert and Training Center for Breast Cancer Screening, Nijmegen, 
